p.blurblarger <b><a href="/about">Bayou-CO2</a></b> provides a simple set of 'free and open source' tools for storage and retrieval of CO2 sensor data, for use with a wide variety of microcontroller hardware.  

li.boxsmaller - Easy to set up
li.boxsmaller - Send data from any device via HTTP POST
li.boxsmaller - Access data as graphs, CSV, or JSON
li.boxsmaller - <a href="">Source code available</a> (GPL 3.0)
li.boxsmaller - Funded on a pay-as-you-can basis via <a href="">Open Collective</a> -- Cheers!

